{"tid":1166413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斥華遊客非法使用 尼泊爾禁支付寶","createTime":"2019-05-22T11:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T12:00:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18f573e5903f5077ea4fc4e1e39647c8a2f23fba","tid":1166413,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:53:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190522/20684353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F20684353&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=1b9b917c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F20684353&h=8cde5eab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190522/20684353</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥華遊客非法使用 尼泊爾禁支付寶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190522/large/china2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190522%2Flarge%2Fchina2.jpg&h=c472fa18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼泊爾《喜馬拉雅時報》昨報道，尼泊爾中央銀行宣佈禁止在尼泊爾使用微信支付和支付寶（圖），直指中國遊客非法使用這些支付應用程式，令尼泊爾流失海外收入，違規遊客將被刑事調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華商毋須繳稅 海外收入流失<br />\n<br />\n報道指，尼泊爾大部份中國遊客都會使用微信支付及支付寶，在尼泊爾經營酒店、餐廳的中國人也愛用這些電子錢包。因此，中國人在尼泊爾遇到同胞經營的店舖時，會選擇使用中國的電子錢包付款。<br />\n<br />\n不過，中國的電子錢包尚未在尼泊爾註冊，意味即使在尼泊爾使用服務，但實際上交易是在中國進行，尼泊爾從未經手這些資金流動，令尼泊爾當局無法將中國遊客的消費登記為海外收入，也意味着華商可以在不繳稅的情況下賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n尼泊爾中央銀行一名不願透露姓名的官員表示，目前至少有兩間尼泊爾公司有興趣充當中間人，幫助尼泊爾當局將中國人的電子錢包消費登記為海外收入。有電子支付專家解釋，當中國相關部門追蹤中國公民是否用正規渠道支付時，才能有效制止非法活動。<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻金服昨呼籲廣大用戶根據《支付寶收錢碼協議》的約定規範使用條碼支付服務，並表示目前支付寶在尼泊爾的跨境業務正常。微信則回應，對於境外違規收款行為，微信支付一直通過技術手段嚴厲打擊。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博/尼泊爾《喜馬拉雅時報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n廣州學校首辦公營「港澳子弟班」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n遭中共迫害滯留台機場 陸異見人士移民加拿大"},{"pid":"c8f77feba68b858dd9becfd39ecd6b445077272c","tid":1166413,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD垃圾國家都踩多你幾腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全地球都無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2774cf6e27ef1aa9a40ce2ddbf1f011517bc8a57","tid":1166413,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f77feba68b858dd9becfd39ecd6b445077272c","tid":1166413,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD垃圾國家都踩多你幾腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全地球都無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"中國抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw屈機男係要捐錢嗰個 定未post千二萬樓契嗰個"},{"pid":"7566e027d90e34ef1a7a173c3e5b89011eb13b81","tid":1166413,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2774cf6e27ef1aa9a40ce2ddbf1f011517bc8a57","tid":1166413,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f77feba68b858dd9becfd39ecd6b445077272c","tid":1166413,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD垃圾國家都踩多你幾腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全地球都無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"中國抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw屈機男係要捐錢嗰個 定未post千二萬樓契嗰個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"我係高登屈機男"}]}